The paper discusses a new type of deep neural network that is capable of dynamic learning and memory, which falls under the category of machine learning. The paper also explores the duality of abstraction and synthesis, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
